                                    <p class="volunteer-details__text">
                                        
                                        The Nepali Roots Summit is an annual gathering of Nepali migrant professionals in Germany, 
                                        primarily hosted in Munich. Our goal is to create a strong, supportive network where knowledge,
                                         experiences, and opportunities are shared to empower the Nepali diaspora. Through inspiring 
                                         talks, workshops, panel discussions, and interactive sessions, we aim to foster collaboration, career
                                        growth, and community development.

                                    </p><!-- /.volunteer-details__text -->

                                    <p class="volunteer-details__text">
                                        
                                        This one-day summit will feature distinguished Nepali professionals from diverse fields, 
                                        each sharing their expertise in short presentations followed by engaging discussions. 
                                        Alongside thought-provoking sessions, the event will include professional networking 
                                        opportunities, workshops and ideas sharing  to connect like-minded individuals. 


                                        The summit offers valuable insights, professional connections, and a platform to celebrate
                                         Nepali talent in Germany. We aim to build a useful & impactful Nepali professional
                                        community, where <b> ideas meet action, and community meets opportunity! </b>
                                    </p>
                                     <p class="volunteer-details__text">
                                      
                                    
                                        <b>
                                            Together, let's shape a vibrant and impactful future for Nepali professionals in Germany.
                                        </b>
                                        
                                     </p>
                                    <p class="volunteer-details__text">
                                        <i>
                                            Note: Diaspora refers to communities of people living outside their country of origin while maintaining cultural ties.
                                        </i>
                                    </p>

                                    <p class="volunteer-details__text">
                                        <i>
                                            Note: Please note that this is a paid event with a fee of X EUR, intended solely to cover the cost of food.
                                        </i>
                                    </p>
                                        
                                    </p><!-- /.volunteer-details__text -->

